  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>3 DIFFERENT GAME MODES</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Main Linear Game:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It features a <strong>linear experience</strong> with a mini story and hidden easter eggs. Find the correct sequence and <strong>don't forget it</strong>! Complete the levels that become more relaxing over time and achieve absolute victory against the simulation. <br><i><u>Includes a special game mode for speedrunning.</u></i><br><i><u></u></i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3551600/extras/2b76f64b76de9fbba68b8d1b62dc7c64.poster.avif?t=1761289298\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3551600/extras/2b76f64b76de9fbba68b8d1b62dc7c64.webm?t=1761289298\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3551600/extras/2b76f64b76de9fbba68b8d1b62dc7c64.mp4?t=1761289298\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Test Your Luck:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is no way to <strong>memorize</strong> the correct path here. Enter randomly generated rooms, take risks, progress, and try to achieve the highest score. <br><i><u>Includes three different difficulty modes.</u></i><br><i><u></u></i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3551600/extras/763a9723c24e3cb513e6e1d966844bfc.poster.avif?t=1761289298\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3551600/extras/763a9723c24e3cb513e6e1d966844bfc.webm?t=1761289298\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3551600/extras/763a9723c24e3cb513e6e1d966844bfc.mp4?t=1761289298\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Waiting Room (2-Player Mode):</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The waiting room mode is designed for <strong>local multiplayer</strong>. Enter the waiting room and enjoy the <strong>thrill of anticipation</strong>! In this completely unpredictable experience, you either win and pass your turn to the other player or face the <strong>scary woman</strong>… Designed for couples and friends to have fun together. <br>Will something <strong>jump out</strong> on the screen? When will it happen? These uncertainties make this mode so <strong>entertaining</strong>!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>3 DIFFERENT GAME MODES</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Main Linear Game:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It features a <strong>linear experience</strong> with a mini story and hidden easter eggs. Find the correct sequence and <strong>don't forget it</strong>! Complete the levels that become more relaxing over time and achieve absolute victory against the simulation. <br><i><u>Includes a special game mode for speedrunning.</u></i><br><i><u></u></i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3551600/extras/2b76f64b76de9fbba68b8d1b62dc7c64.poster.avif?t=1761289298\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3551600/extras/2b76f64b76de9fbba68b8d1b62dc7c64.webm?t=1761289298\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3551600/extras/2b76f64b76de9fbba68b8d1b62dc7c64.mp4?t=1761289298\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Test Your Luck:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is no way to <strong>memorize</strong> the correct path here. Enter randomly generated rooms, take risks, progress, and try to achieve the highest score. <br><i><u>Includes three different difficulty modes.</u></i><br><i><u></u></i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3551600/extras/763a9723c24e3cb513e6e1d966844bfc.poster.avif?t=1761289298\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3551600/extras/763a9723c24e3cb513e6e1d966844bfc.webm?t=1761289298\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3551600/extras/763a9723c24e3cb513e6e1d966844bfc.mp4?t=1761289298\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Waiting Room (2-Player Mode):</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The waiting room mode is designed for <strong>local multiplayer</strong>. Enter the waiting room and enjoy the <strong>thrill of anticipation</strong>! In this completely unpredictable experience, you either win and pass your turn to the other player or face the <strong>scary woman</strong>… Designed for couples and friends to have fun together. <br>Will something <strong>jump out</strong> on the screen? When will it happen? These uncertainties make this mode so <strong>entertaining</strong>!</p>",
